snippet.title: Spider-Man 3: The Game - E3 2006 Teaser
snippet.description:
Date: May 12th, 2006

The 2006 Electronic Entertainment Expo (E3) took place at the Los Angeles Convention Center in Los Angeles, California on May 10-12. (Giant Bomb)

Intense teaser trailer for the 2007 movie tie-in game 'Spider-Man 3', showing off the then impressive in-game player model.
